  {
    "row": 7,
    "rowsha": "iiTglm2472SUOiC6SSzJU/N5a8coKiGOtvWLQHmeybQ=",
    "originContent": "## What Is This Card Deck About?  ",
    "translatedContent": "## このカードデッキは何ですか？  "
  },
  {
    "row": 8,
    "rowsha": "ssTOtY5FfIXYHgVYLAINwDTb+ovHa/j87QnhdyHGyz4=",
    "originContent": "The WCAG 2.2 Card Deck startet as weekend project to combine multiple great accessibility resources into a single toolkit:  ",
    "translatedContent": "WCAG 2.2カードデッキは、週末のプロジェクトとして複数の優れたアクセシビリティリソースを単一のツールキットにまとめるために始まりました：  "
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "0O4OdRlF4Swh4mwgCSyuPCmmaa/HKyMQm3aNDJTOlaE=",
    "originContent": "- a summary of all WCAG 2.2 success criteria",
    "translatedContent": "- WCAG 2.2の全成功基準の要約  "
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "fqUEHJJNAYxZN4JJD3PxZZxmvGXtDpORcTRtXmGS+Ik=",
    "originContent": "- in easy to understand descriptions",
    "translatedContent": "- 理解しやすい説明で  "
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "uInRS+J7Ly2XvJJLNawAhxnn4bHbM3BQSVNRgHL77ao=",
    "originContent": "- grouped by practical theme for testing (based on '[WCAG 2.2 map by theme](https://andrewhick.com/accessibility/wcag-map/)', '[WCAG 2.2 map by theme - AAA version](https://andrewhick.com/aaa/)' and '[WCAG decision tree](https://github.com/andrewhick/accessibility/wiki/WCAG-decision-tree)' by Andrew Hick)",
    "translatedContent": "- 実用的なテーマごとにテスト用にグループ化（'[WCAG 2.2 map by theme](https://andrewhick.com/accessibility/wcag-map/)', '[WCAG 2.2 map by theme - AAA version](https://andrewhick.com/aaa/)', '[WCAG decision tree](https://github.com/andrewhick/accessibility/wiki/WCAG-decision-tree)' Andrew Hickによる）  "
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "diTybU2MYtRclf2hu+yVr4QfiDyfocV8Pa6lA9vWSEU=",
    "originContent": "- including indicators who benefits from meeting each criterion (based on [Atomic A11Y](https://www.atomica11y.com/) by Charlie Triplett, [Appt.org](https://appt.org/en/), and [IBM accessibility requirements](https://www.ibm.com/able/requirements/requirements/))",
    "translatedContent": "- 各基準を満たすことで恩恵を受ける人を示す指標を含む（Charlie Triplettの[Atomic A11Y](https://www.atomica11y.com/)、[Appt.org](https://appt.org/en/)、[IBMアクセシビリティ要件](https://www.ibm.com/able/requirements/requirements/)に基づく）  "
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "7fEmCrSlgnbPV2Zzy86U91lx/D3Wj3E3i5RN2Cp1WK4=",
    "originContent": "- highlighting which roles are primarily responsible (based on the GOV.UK [WCAG Primer](https://alphagov.github.io/wcag-primer/), and the '[Accessibility Responsibilities by Project Role](https://www.unimelb.edu.au/accessibility/project-management-old/responsibility-breakdown/print-version)' checklist from the University of Melbourne)",
    "translatedContent": "- 主に責任を持つ役割を強調（GOV.UKの[WCAG Primer](https://alphagov.github.io/wcag-primer/)、メルボルン大学の'[Accessibility Responsibilities by Project Role](https://www.unimelb.edu.au/accessibility/project-management-old/responsibility-breakdown/print-version)'チェックリストに基づく）  "
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "nAbp0b/uJSGNrZpAAU+pe38271PJXk3M3KCVHz485g0=",
    "originContent": "- suggesting which success criteria work best together",
    "translatedContent": "- 一緒に機能する成功基準の提案  "
  },
  {
