  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "lbQxrcvPgCi3l0axJ8hoNm94BCpvmpmTGgKYc3cSW5Q=",
    "originContent": "## What's Up Next?  ",
    "translatedContent": "## 今後の予定は？  "
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "Nsxt7ZNx/Oqy8WS8AMykaA/B/Sfmj+WmUR+RWNLp2eY=",
    "originContent": "Thanks to amazing feedback after my initial announcement on LinkedIn, I already have a list of features that I am planning to add in future versions:  ",
    "translatedContent": "LinkedInでの初回発表後の素晴らしいフィードバックのおかげで、将来のバージョンに追加予定の機能リストがあります：  "
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "ybI2oqo4yTgdTt2fDkQUdp+WUZex2v2rC4wOfJvj4k0=",
    "originContent": "- More languages (already planned: Japanese, Arabian, Swedish, Norwegian, Catalan - more to come)",
    "translatedContent": "- 多言語対応（既に計画中：日本語、アラビア語、スウェーデン語、ノルウェー語、カタルーニャ語 - 今後も増加予定）  "
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "OmFyr07VqDdoDgCGflhfK+dNwO07LylIK9+ZSClOPQA=",
    "originContent": "- Add method descriptions (how to get most out of the card deck - e.g. for training/learning, or accessibility audits)",
    "translatedContent": "- 方法の説明追加（カードデッキを最大限活用する方法 - 例：トレーニング/学習やアクセシビリティ監査向け）  "
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "pwOffBdwldVQiezLAPYfwMeAp8Bjk6fPEe4PSLIdbLA=",
    "originContent": "- Add tools that can be used to test for each success criteria (including relevant external sources)",
    "translatedContent": "- 各成功基準のテストに使えるツールの追加（関連外部ソースも含む）  "
  },
  {
